      "source": [
        "#  ClimaShield — Random Forest Model (SAFE / HEAT / THIRST)\n",
        "### Smart Rooftop Garden Guardian\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook trains, evaluates, and exports the on-device Random Forest classifier that powers ClimaShield's offline decision core.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Pipeline:**\n",
        "1. Load & explore the dataset\n",
        "2. Clean & validate features\n",
        "3. Train/test split\n",
        "4. Train the Random Forest\n",
        "5. Evaluate (accuracy, precision/recall/F1, confusion matrix, ROC, cross-validation)\n",
        "6. Feature importance (explainability for judges)\n",
        "7. Hyperparameter tuning (optional)\n",
        "8. Export the trained model (`.joblib`) for the Raspberry Pi\n",
        "\n",
        "**Input features:** `Air_Temp_C`, `Air_Humidity_Pct`, `Solar_Radiation_W_m2`, `Soil_Moisture_Pct`, `Root_Temp_C`, `VPD_kPa`, `Tank_Level_Pct`\n",
        "**Output label:** `SAFE` / `HEAT` / `THIRST`\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "093a5911",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "093a5911"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 1. Setup — Install & Import Libraries"
      ]
    },
