        "### ROC Curves (One-vs-Rest)\n",
        "\n",
        "ROC/AUC is naturally a binary-classification metric. For our 3-class problem we use the One-vs-Rest (OvR) approach: each class is evaluated against \"all other classes combined.\"\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 19,
      "id": "2eab2880",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
