        "\n",
        "Grid search over a small, sensible parameter space. This step can take a minute or two on Colab's free CPU.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 25,
      "id": "4a0b771d",
      "metadata": {
